episodes.title: YouTube's Hidden Cult - AllatRa
episodes.description:
Over the past few years, a group known as AllatRa has grown to be more well-known. Meeting high ranking individuals around the world, such as the pope, claiming to be your average climate change activists. However under the surface, AllatRa has an extremely suspicious and concerning background. In this video we dive into the AllatRa rabbit hole. From a shady puppet with "unreliable" credentials, to a man currently being (allegedly) defamed across the internet, this is YouTube's Hidden Cult - AllatRa.

episodes.title: Joan Ocean & The Crazy Hippie Dolphin Cult
episodes.description:
